name: Jagath Paruchuri
text: Clean. A bit pricey due to downtown location but well worth it. Clean, hot food and a gracious staff

name: Poptographix
text: Yeah it's nothing special but it's way better than anything in the surrounding area. Cheap compared to the miserable touristy restaurants near. Staff are friendly and area is a chill and quiet place. Food is alright.

text: It's a little expensive ($10 for a slice, 2 bread sticks, and a drink) and the food is poor quality. The pizza was greasy, the bread sticks were doughy, and both were completely lacking in flavor.
